This code was developed for http://www.schwarz-bunte-seiten-berlin.org/
"Schwarz-Bunte-Seiten-Berlin" is a project done by a group of the Anarchist Federation of Berlin http://afb.blogsport.de/

You are welcome use this in your Federation/region and to contribute.



System requirements
--------------------
PHP and SQL-Database


Installation
-------------
1) create the database with db.sql
2) configurate
    - replace TEX/header.png and TEX/imprint.png with your logo and address
    - edit protected/mysql.inc and create .htaccess file for "protected"-folder (only admin should have password)
    - cp locale.php_template to locale.php and edit the texts as you need
3) create .htaccess file for the "organize"-folder (only content editors should have password)
4) copy all files but mysql.inc to webserver


Usage
-----
http://yourdomain/organize -> password protected area for editing the data. You can copy and paste all websites and all e-mail-contacts from the bottom of this page.



Maintenance
--------------
* Logos of entries have to be put to TEX manually
* Use check_for_broken_links.sh from times to times. Unfortunately you check the information at least every year manually as adresses and contact data change quickly.
